lead_paragraph: Jaysean Paige had 14 points and No. 10 West Virginia wrapped up second place in the Big 12 Conference with a 69-58 victory at No. 19 Baylor on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: No. 10 West Virginia 2nd in Big 12 With Win at No. 19 Baylor
